Package: FacileAnalysis
Type: Package
Title: Analysis routines over a FacileDataStore
Version: 0.1.6
Authors@R: c(
    person("Steve", "Lianoglou", , "lianoglou@dnli.com", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Denali Therapeutics", role = c("cph", "fnd")))
Description: Provides modularized versions of analyses that are commonly
    performed over genomics data. Analysis results can be interactively explored
    by analysts using the "vizualize" or "shine" functions, and embedded into
    Rmarkdown reports using their respective "report" functions.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    broom,
    checkmate,
    crosstalk,
    DT,
    edgeR,
